comments: Gordon (DEN) places his forearm against Saric's (GSW) upper body but the contact is marginal and does not prevent him from controlling the rebound.
Curry's (GSW) shot attempt does not make contact with the rim and the shot clock expires before Paul (GSW) releases his shot attempt.
Jokic (DEN) establishes screening position in Curry's (GSW) path and marginal contact occurs as he defends over the pick.
Saric (GSW) immediately slides his hand off of Murray's (DEN) side as he establishes screening position and marginal contact occurs as Murray defends over the screen.
Gordon (DEN) clamps and holds Saric's (GSW) left arm and affects his ability to control the rebound.
Jokic (DEN) slightly raises his right knee as he establishes himself in Wiggins' (GSW) path and marginal contact occurs to Wiggins' side as the screen is set.
Saric (GSW) maintains a legal guarding position during Jokic's (DEN) post move and shot attempt.
Paul (GSW) leans into Caldwell-Pope (DEN) as the two players briefly engage and disengage.
Looney (GSW) maintains a legal guarding position as he contests Jokic's (DEN) jump shot attempt.
